description: LE Lundbergföretagen AB is an investment company, which engages in managing and developing other companies. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 3,287 full-time employees.  The firm is engaged in the management and development of a number of companies, by means of active and long-term ownership. Its investment portfolio includes the wholly owned unlisted real estate company, Fastighets AB L E Lundberg, and the publicly traded subsidiaries, Holmen and Hufvudstaden. The firm also has major shareholdings in Handelsbanken, Husqvarna, Industrivarden, Indutrade and Sandvik, as well as held shares in Skanska. Additionally, the Company operates a wholly owned subsidiary, L E Lundberg Kapitalforvaltning AB, which is engaged in securities trading.
